You probably don't want to do this -- yield() means "put me at the
tail of the runqueue."  I think cond_resched() is more likely what you
want.
 > +#endif
 > +/* END_NOSHIP_TO_OPENIB */
uhh... and I don't see an #if to match that #endif.
